Cons:. waiting for satellites, speed in question. 
Summary:. This is the ultimate training tool! I can do anything and everything that you could ask for and puts it in a chart and graph for you. The only reason I gave it 9 instead of 10 is that sometimes it seems that the speed measurement is off. I'll have to delve deeper into that issue. This is an awesome product. Also, I found if for $249.99 (look hard).. 

