Pros:. I liked this product very mucn until it died suddenly and for no reason.. 
Cons:. I was happy with the Garmin until it died on me, in the middle of my 1st marathon (after 27 km). Apparently it lost satellite reception.. After contacting customer support, I reinstalled the SW but it continued to not find the satellite reception.. 
Summary:. Garmin Customer support suggested that I pay MORE good money to purchase their faulty and unreliable product, without being helpful and giving any decent suggestions. Of course - I found more help online than from Garmin product support. Sounds to me like they are more interested in making more money than supporting their customers.. Recommendation: Find a better product.. 

